1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:58,719
You summoned me here today.

4
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:00,560
Surely it's not just to say all this.

5
00:01:02,039 --> 00:01:03,159
I know

6
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,920
that after today,

7
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,239
you and I will part ways.

8
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:09,359
So,

9
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:11,680
I want to play one more piece

10
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:15,799
for you today.

11
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,159
Right now,

12
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:21,120
I am not the Emperor,

13
00:01:22,159 --> 00:01:23,640
and you are not Lord Nine-Thousand.

14
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:10,680
(You broke such a precious vase.)

15
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:13,759
(I'll tear out your tendons)

16
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:16,080
(and flay your skin!)

17
00:02:16,319 --> 00:02:17,199
(Stop!)

18
00:02:20,039 --> 00:02:21,479
(Don't hit him anymore.)

19
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:22,520
(I'll go with you.)

20
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,360
(You kept your promise to me.)

21
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,680
(Once I take the throne,)

22
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,319
(the first thing I'll do)

23
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,840
(is avenge you.)

24
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:01,879
Wait.

25
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:04,840
Back then,

26
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:07,080
in that forsaken palace,

27
00:04:07,639 --> 00:04:09,879
you and I killed that old eunuch
together.

28
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,639
From that day on, we were like brothers.

29
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:13,719
Does that mean nothing

30
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:15,879
compared to

31
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,759
the few months you've had
with Jiang Yukui?

32
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,040
After all this time,

33
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,319
you still think we're parting ways

34
00:04:23,319 --> 00:04:25,040
because of Jiang Yukui?

35
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,160
All these years,

36
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,480
how many wrongs have you committed?

37
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,439
You know that.

38
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,839
You were wrong,

39
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,839
and so was I.

40
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,399
Aren't you curious?

41
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,319
Your family was always neutral,

42
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:53,319
posing no threat to the Rong family's
position.

43
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:55,279
Why did Rong Xiu massacre
your entire clan?

44
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,560
The one who truly ordered
the destruction of your family

45
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,480
was that scumbag, the late Emperor.

46
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:09,079
These are that scumbag's
personal diaries.

47
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:11,040
They contain secret letters
he sent to Rong Xiu.

48
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,879
Back then,

49
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:15,480
he coveted your mother's beauty.

50
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,800
He found an excuse
to throw your father in prison.

51
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:20,000
When your mother came
to the palace to plead for him,

52
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,920
he took the chance and violated her.

53
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,079
Later,

54
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:25,079
your mother became pregnant

55
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,079
and gave birth to you.

56
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,959
The old fool counted the months

57
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,480
and knew you were his child.

58
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,000
He planned to bring you back.

59
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,399
He even had a diviner pick
an auspicious time.

60
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:35,920
But the diviner said

61
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,600
you carried a doomed fate.

62
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,240
That you were born to bring him ruin.

63
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,079
In a rage, that scumbag

64
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,639
ordered Rong Xiu

65
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:44,079
to wipe out your entire family.

66
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,680
I always thought we were like brothers.

67
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,120
Turns out

68
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,720
we really are brothers.

69
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,399
Shut up!

70
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,000
Now,

71
00:06:03,519 --> 00:06:05,879
I am your only living kin in this world.

72
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,079
Why?

73
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:14,240
Why did you know everything all along

74
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,759
and only tell me now?

75
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,800
You knew

76
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,800
I've been hunting Rong Xiu
all these years

77
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,240
because I believed

78
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:23,879
he was the one who destroyed my family.

79
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,920
I never expected

80
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:31,360
the true culprit to be me.

81
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:32,959
Actually,

82
00:06:33,839 --> 00:06:35,240
you don't need to feel sad

83
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,680
about who you are.

84
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,839
You should feel honored.

85
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:39,079
He was a scumbag!

86
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,839
A scumbag, you understand?

87
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:41,920
A scumbag!

88
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,040
Now I finally know

89
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,879
why my mother, when I was young,

90
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,959
always looked at me

91
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:53,480
with such sorrow in her eyes.

92
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:01,000
So I was her lifelong shame.

93
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:03,800
And my father died for me.

94
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,680
No.

95
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,600
He's not your father.

96
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,079
I...

97
00:07:09,879 --> 00:07:11,639
I am your family.

98
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:12,680
Go on.

99
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,199
If beating me to death

100
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:15,560
will make you acknowledge what we are,

101
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,199
then do it.

102
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:16,639
Hit me!

103
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:17,519
Kill me now.

104
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,319
Kill me!

105
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,000
Kill me!

106
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,279
I knew it.

107
00:07:29,279 --> 00:07:31,279
You couldn't bring yourself to hurt me.

108
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:32,639
My brother.

109
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:56,959
Father.

110
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,000
Mother.

111
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,439
How could there be

112
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:07,480
such a cruel twist of fate?

113
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:10,079
I devoted myself to revenge,

114
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:12,920
but in the end, I lost my way.

115
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,800
Please guide me, Father, Mother.

116
00:08:19,199 --> 00:08:20,439
Should I

117
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:22,319
let go of this obsession?

118
00:08:25,639 --> 00:08:26,240
My Lord.

119
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,879
Is Yukui in trouble?

120
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:35,799
The Holy Maiden...

121
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,200
We lost her.

122
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:01,879
Who are you?

123
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,159
How dare you block His Majesty's path?

124
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:18,559
So alike, truly, so alike.

125
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:51,840
Aren't you afraid?

126
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:54,120
The Divine Power,

127
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,960
if it could truly take my life,

128
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:58,200
you would have used it long ago.

129
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,240
Back then,

130
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,279
when Yusang tried to use
the Divine Power on me,

131
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:02,639
she told me

132
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:04,159
that the Divine Power,

133
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:06,200
against those of royal blood,

134
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,919
can only strengthen them.

135
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:09,840
It cannot take or control.

136
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,120
Isn't that right?

137
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:15,519
Who said I came to kill you?

138
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,320
I came to make a deal.

139
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,759
You've gone to such lengths

140
00:10:20,759 --> 00:10:22,440
to obtain the Divine Power.

141
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,559
Surely

142
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,720
it's not just for pleasure.

143
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:30,000
Whatever you desire,

144
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:34,960
I can help you attain it.

145
00:10:41,559 --> 00:10:42,320
Come on.

146
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,120
Show me

147
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,919
what else you've got

148
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:47,360
to amuse me.

149
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,120
Beyond our borders,

150
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,480
the barbarian tribes

151
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:58,120
are burning our supplies
and raiding our convoys,

152
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,519
growing restless.

153
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:00,720
Within,

154
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:03,240
Prince Zhu Heng has gathered
rebel forces

155
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,600
and plans to revolt.

156
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:06,840
General Rong Xiu is dead.

157
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:10,600
I can help you turn the tide.

158
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,720
You?

159
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,759
How can you help me?

160
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:18,480
Send the Zhao Tribe to the frontier
to fight the barbarians.

161
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,679
Your troops

162
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:21,120
can then stay here

163
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,960
to hold off Zhu Heng's rebels.

164
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,000
The Zhao Tribe,

165
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,000
though a vassal of Kun,

166
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,200
still harbors disloyalty.

167
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,919
If they're sent to the frontier,

168
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:31,799
how can I trust them to fight

169
00:11:31,799 --> 00:11:33,000
like my Kun warriors?

170
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,519
I have a plan

171
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:36,840
that will force the Zhao Tribe
to fight with their backs to the wall.

172
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,279
Of course.

173
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:46,480
You'll have to pay the same price.

174
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,519
I want one person's life.

175
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,600
You

176
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,480
want mine?

177
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,559
No, Rong Zhaohua's.

178
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,360
What?

179
00:12:10,879 --> 00:12:12,360
Can't bear to part with her?

180
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,200
I never expected you

181
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:18,879
to actually have feelings
for Rong Zhaohua.

182
00:12:19,639 --> 00:12:21,879
But for someone like you,

183
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,279
that's not a good thing.

184
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,840
To you,

185
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,559
everyone in this world

186
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:34,600
is just a stepping stone.

187
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,399
Rong Xiu.

188
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:39,279
Lord Nine-Thousand.

189
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,759
My elder sister.

190
00:12:42,679 --> 00:12:44,679
You would discard any of them

191
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:47,399
once they threaten your throne.

192
00:12:48,279 --> 00:12:50,360
But once you have a true heart,

193
00:12:51,279 --> 00:12:52,759
you have a weakness.

194
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:53,320
No!

195
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,559
I have no weakness.

196
00:12:55,919 --> 00:12:57,279
I can agree

197
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:58,960
to give you Zhaohua.

198
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:01,679
But I have one condition.

199
00:13:01,679 --> 00:13:03,159
She is about to give birth.

200
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:04,279
Your elder sister

201
00:13:04,279 --> 00:13:05,559
was killed by her.

202
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,240
But this

203
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:09,039
has nothing to do with her child.

204
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:11,879
Once she has given birth,

205
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:13,159
I will hand her over

206
00:13:13,879 --> 00:13:14,960
to you.

207
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,399
My sister was kind.

208
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:19,360
She would not have wanted
an innocent life to be harmed.

209
00:13:22,399 --> 00:13:23,519
I accept.

210
00:13:46,420 --> 00:13:47,820
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

211
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:49,740
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

212
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:53,060
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

213
00:13:53,380 --> 00:13:57,180
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

214
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:01,860
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

215
00:14:01,860 --> 00:14:03,380
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

216
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:07,140
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

217
00:14:07,140 --> 00:14:11,140
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

218
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:15,460
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

219
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:19,020
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

220
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:21,340
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

221
00:14:21,340 --> 00:14:25,540
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

222
00:14:25,980 --> 00:14:27,620
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

223
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:29,140
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

224
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:32,340
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

225
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:34,660
♪In dreams, it's you♪

226
00:14:34,660 --> 00:14:36,060
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

227
00:14:36,060 --> 00:14:39,380
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

228
00:14:39,380 --> 00:14:42,780
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

229
00:14:42,780 --> 00:14:46,340
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

230
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:49,580
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

231
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:53,020
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
